&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;As a VP, Client Partner, you lead delivery and growth on assigned enterprise engagements: owning the work itself, deepening client trust, and contributing to the firm’s offerings and IP. You work alongside SVP, Client Partners on broader strategy and pursuits.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
